### AYYUAZ.APP Login Probleminin Həlli - Test Sırası

# 1. API-nin işləməsini yoxla
GET https://localhost:7038/api/health

### 2. AuthController debug endpoint-ini yoxla  
GET https://localhost:7038/api/auth/debug

### 3. Database bağlantısını yoxla
GET https://localhost:7038/api/health/database

### 4. Seeded admin user ilə giriş test et
POST https://localhost:7038/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Admin045@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. Validation test et - boş data
POST https://localhost:7038/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "",
    "password": ""
}

### 6. Validation test et - yanlış format
POST https://localhost:7038/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "invalid-email",
    "password": "123"
}

### 7. Mövcud olmayan user
POST https://localhost:7038/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "nonexistent@test.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 8. Yanlış password
POST https://localhost:7038/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Admin045@gmail.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}